&lt;h2 id="exception-handling-and-troubleshooting"&gt;Exception Handling and Troubleshooting
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Throughput degradation during buffet congestion:&lt;/b&gt; Latency at live stations can be reduced by entering before 18:00, avoiding peak times (~19:00).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Open-air section restrictions due to weather:&lt;/b&gt; In the event of high winds or precipitation, flow to indoor sections is automatically executed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
